/*
 * control galvo mirrors using 2 MCP4725 DACs
 * 
 * MCP4725
 * 5.93Hz sine wave
 * 
 *  VCC   GND  Vout
 *    |    |    |
 * |---------------|
 * |     AJW0      |
 * |---------------|
 *    |    |    |
 *   SDA  CLK   A0
 * 
 * circuit board:
 * smoothing capacitor
 * pullup for SDA/SCL (pads on bottom [connected])
 * pullup/pulldown for A0 (pads on top [disconnected]) => sets Adress
 * A0=GND: Adress=0x60 /// A0=VCC: Adress=0x61
 * 
 */

